OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than
OL,4,Cexpected as Ofgem increases price cap
OL,6,FOfgem changes the price cap for
OL,7,Fhouseholds every three months. The new
OL,8,Fprice cap will run from April 1 until
OL,9,FJuly.
OL,11,FIn practice, most people will pay less
OL,12,Fto their energy suppliers in the
OL,13,Fspring and summer months, because
OL,14,Fhouseholds typically use less energy
OL,15,Fthen.
