OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than
OL,4,Cexpected as Ofgem increases price cap
OL,6,FDebt charity StepChange have seen a
OL,7,Frise in people asking for help with
OL,8,Fenergy arrears. Almost one in three
OL,9,F(31%) of people are worried about
OL,10,Fpaying their energy bills over the
OL,11,Fnext six months, according to research
OL,12,Fcarried out by YouGov for StepChange.
OL,14,FThis rises to 37% of parents with
OL,15,Fchildren under 18.
OL,17,FAround two in five (42%) of private
OL,18,Frenters are worried about paying their
OL,19,Fenergy bills over the next six months.
