OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than
OL,4,Cexpected as Ofgem increases price cap
OL,6,FMore than half (56%) of people on
OL,7,FUniversal Credit are worried about
OL,8,Fpaying their energy bills over the
OL,9,Fnext six months.
OL,11,FRichard Lane, from the debt charity
OL,12,FStepChange, said: "Ultimately what's
OL,13,Fhappened is that people have exhausted
OL,14,Ftheir financial resilience, they've
OL,15,Fcut back, they've maybe changed their
OL,16,Fsupermarket brand they shop with,
OL,17,Fthey've used up their savings and what
OL,18,Fpeople are telling us is they've got
OL,19,Fnothing else to cut back on."
