OL,4,Cexpected as Ofgem increases price cap
OL,6,FRichard Lane, from the debt charity
OL,7,FStepChange shared tips with ITV News:
OL,9,FOfgem Chief Executive Jonathan
OL,10,FBrearley said: "We know that no price
OL,11,Frise is ever welcome, and that the
OL,12,Fcost of energy remains a huge
OL,13,Fchallenge for many households".
OL,15,F"But our reliance on international gas
OL,16,Fmarkets leads to volatile wholesale
OL,17,Fprices, and continues to drive up
OL,18,Fbills, which is why it's more
OL,19,Fimportant than ever that we're driving
OL,20,Fforward investment in a cleaner,
OL,21,Fhomegrown system."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
