OL,4,Cexpected as Ofgem increases price cap
OL,6,FHe added that those worried about
OL,7,Fpaying their energy bills should reach
OL,8,Fout to their supplier: "Where
OL,9,Fpossible, switching or fixing tariffs
OL,10,Fnow could also help to bring costs
OL,11,Fdown and provide certainty over coming
OL,12,Fpayments," he said.
OL,14,FThe latest increase in the price cap
OL,15,Fmarks the third consecutive time costs
OL,16,Fhave risen in recent quarters, coming
OL,17,Fas a blow to Labour's election promise
OL,18,Fof reducing bills by "up to #300 by
OL,19,F2030."
