OL,12,Ffrom the grip of fossil fuel markets,"
OL,13,Fhe said, "Expanding the warm home
OL,14,Fdiscount can help protect millions of
OL,15,Ffamilies from rising energy bills,
OL,16,Foffering support to consumers across
OL,17,Fthe country."
