OL,6,F"I wouldn't fix until this afternoon,
OL,7,Fas there are some cheaper tariffs
OL,8,Fcoming online," said Martin Lewis.
OL,10,F"When you do a comparison, get
OL,11,Fyourself on a comparison site, because
OL,12,Fyour cheapest depends on where you
OL,13,Flive and how much you use.
OL,15,F"If you're going to do a comparison,
OL,16,Fget yourself on a whole-of-market by
OL,17,Fdefault comparison site," he added.
