OL,6,FThe energy price rises come at a time
OL,7,Fwhere household budgets are already
OL,8,Ffacing a squeeze and they won't be the
OL,9,Fonly bills going up this April.
OL,11,FEarlier this year it was announced the
OL,12,Faverage family's water bill will rise
OL,13,Fby about #120, although this figure
OL,14,Fvaries depending on where you live.
OL,16,FCouncil tax bills are also set to rise
OL,17,Fat the same time with most councils in
OL,18,FEngland increasing them by at least
OL,19,F4.99%. This will see council tax bills
OL,20,Fin England rise by an average of
OL,21,F#108.33.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
